@startuml
!theme plain
title Control Pilot Synchronized ADC Sampling

participant "CTIMER3" as TIMER
participant "Match 1\n(ADC Trigger)" as M1
participant "ADC" as ADC
participant "CP Signal" as CP

== PWM Cycle ==
TIMER -> CP: PWM High (Start)
note right of CP: Voltage depends on\nvehicle state:\n12V, 9V, 6V, 3V

TIMER -> TIMER: Calculate optimal\nsampling point
note left of TIMER: Sample at middle of\nhigh or low pulse\nfor stable reading

TIMER -> M1: Match 1 triggers
M1 -> ADC: Start conversion
ADC -> ADC: Sample CP voltage
ADC -> ADC: 16-bit conversion
ADC --> ADC: Generate interrupt
note right of ADC: Store value in\ns_u16AdcCPRawValue

TIMER -> CP: PWM Low
note right of CP: Continue PWM cycle

@enduml
